      "rating": 5,
      "relative_time_description": "4 years ago",
      "text": "We recently moved into a new house that needed some electrical repairs. Nathan came highly recommend so we scheduled an appointment. Couldn't have been happier. He arrived on time and was an absolute pleasure to deal with. He was professional and quickly fixed the issues we had in the house. Being new to the area it feels good to have found our go-to for electrical work. Highly recommended.",
